se.jguru.nazgul.core.xmlbinding.spi.jaxb.transport.type

Class AbstractJaxbAnnotatedTransportType<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.jguru.nazgul.core.xmlbinding.spi.jaxb.transport.type.AbstractJaxbAnnotatedTransportType<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable, ClassInformationHolder
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JaxbAnnotatedCollection, JaxbAnnotatedDateTime

    public abstract class AbstractJaxbAnnotatedTransportType<T>
extends Object
implements ClassInformationHolder, Serializable, Comparable
    Abstract supertype of JAXB-annotated transport types, implying that all subtypes should implement ClassInformationHolder and Serializable.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
    See Also:
